description: Come help out the women get back on their feet by offering childcare services. Play with the kids, help with homework after school, and more!

Looking for a new and transformational role that will be life changing for our residents AND you? Ready to make a year-long commitment to walk with, mentor and coach a man as he progresses through the program?

Looking for a new and transformational role that will be life changing for our residents AND you? Ready to make a year-long commitment to walk with, mentor and coach a woman as she progresses through the program?

The program is looking for volunteers who can provide structured child-learning care to infants and toddlers while their mother is attending a class or a support group. Your help as a volunteer will allow the women to really focus on the discussion during the session.
